201
00:14:17,513 --> 00:14:21,392
All right, sergeant. Have them fall in
according to height, right to left.

202
00:14:24,913 --> 00:14:26,744
According to height, fall in!

203
00:14:26,953 --> 00:14:30,628
Come on, you jokers, you heard him.
Get in there! Fall in line!

204
00:14:34,193 --> 00:14:37,344
-Come on, move!
-Come on, come on. Turn around.

205
00:14:37,553 --> 00:14:39,987
Come on, here! I said, get in line.

206
00:14:44,193 --> 00:14:46,149
Straighten up your jacket there.

207
00:14:46,313 --> 00:14:47,905
Get over there.

208
00:14:49,433 --> 00:14:53,267
-All right, have them count off.
-Sir. Count off!

209
00:15:01,633 --> 00:15:04,147
Let's see what they can do
with a little close-order.

210
00:15:04,353 --> 00:15:07,345
-Hut, right!
-Right.

211
00:15:10,393 --> 00:15:12,987
Left, march!

212
00:15:14,473 --> 00:15:18,227
Hut, hut, hut, hut.

213
00:15:18,513 --> 00:15:23,507
Two, three, four, hut, hut, hut.
Two, three.

214
00:15:32,193 --> 00:15:34,149
Squad, halt!

215
